channel.title: Player's can't connect?
channel.description:
Hi guys,
So lately(yesterday), my server was working fine...had 16 online... But like 20 minutes ago...my friend was complaining to me that he couldn't connect. I thought this was a joke, since I'm on my server right now. I TeamViewered him, and some message pops up and says "Error. Click here for details" with a white background. What happened?? Everything was fine yesterday, and I'm on my server right now! Please help me.. :(
Thanks in advance,
PaTTT :D
